### Update - name only
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products/categories/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Electronics & Tech"
}

### Update - deactivate
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products/categories/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "active": false
}

### Update - reactivate
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products/categories/13
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "active": true
}

### Update - display order only
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products/categories/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "display-order": 5
}

### Update - all fields including parent
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products/categories/2
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Computers, Laptops & Tablets",
  "active": true,
  "display-order": 2,
  "parent-id": 1
}

### Update - validation error: blank name
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products/categories/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "",
  "active": true,
  "display-order": 1
}

### Update - not found (EntityNotFoundException)
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products/categories/999
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Does Not Exist",
  "active": true,
  "display-order": 1
}